description: algoseek provides historical intraday and EOD market data for all US listed and delisted Equities, ETFs, ETNs, ADRs and Warrants from January 2007 to present. Data is collected from the full SIP (Securities Information Processors) feed via our NY4 co-lo servers, including all trades and quotes published to every exchange as well as FINRA.
